\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13263722 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7406736\charrsid10123639 Your grandfather just upped and left them?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3288297 FW  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7406736\charrsid10123639 That's it.
