\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13263722 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7406736\charrsid10123639 Did your parents tell you to hit back or not if another child hurt you?
